    <h1>Deep Learning</h1>
    <p class="description">A machine-learning technique that uses <strong>multi-layered neural networks</strong> to learn patterns from data automatically. It powers Google's search algorithms, generative AI, and nearly every marketing personalisation system you already use.</p>
